Silas KENDRICKS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DESOTO CORRECTIONAL INST., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4756 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 31, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petition for writ of habeas corpus is hereby transferred to the Circuit Court of the Fourth Judicial Circuit in and for Duval County, Florida, case number 2005-CF-4840.

CASANUEVA, LUCAS, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
